  <brief_title>Intraoperative Mechanical Ventilation and Postoperative Pulmonary Complications After On-pump Cardiac Surgery in High-risk Patients</brief_title>
  <acronym>VACARM</acronym>
  <official_title>Effect of IntraoperatiVe High Positive End-ExpirAtory Pressure (PEEP) With ReCruitment MAneuveRs vs Low PEEP on Major Postoperative Pulmonary Complications and Death After On-pump Cardiac Surgery in High-risk Patients: the VACARM Study</official_title>
